data.description:
Serene Lake views the minute you enter the foyer and throughout this breathtaking home. This large and spacious home is close to Blue Mtn Beach and Gulf Place public access points.    The large lot will accommodate a pool.  New Beach colors exterior painted white brick (4sides) w/ decorative front featuring brick water table w/ Hardi Board & Batten (with beach serene colors) The home features 5 bedrooms & 3 baths divided into 3 separate suite areas.  A dedicated office/study or 2nd living area opens off the foyer with an additional banquet sized formal dining room. Open to the great room and made for entertaining is the extra-large kitchen, featuring a center island, huge walk-in pantry, multiple prep stations, lake front dining area & high coffered high ceilings. Meticulously maintained and with a new A/C this home is ready for you to move in.  Make this your new beach home and enjoy the large space and great value within an easy drive to Topsail Park, 30A beaches, and miles and miles of South Walton bike trails.

Enjoy water views bringing nature into your life with visiting ducks. This home is a short drive to West side of 30A and beach access points. Come live the 30A Sowal life of white sands, blue/green clear water, great dining, excellent casual dining, golf, tennis, boating, and relaxing.   Sandestin, Santa Rosa Beach, Seaside, Seagrove, the Bay in this wonderful neighborhood.  Only 2.7 miles to Ed Walline Gulf Place Beach Access.
